    <h1 class="col-start-4 col-span-6 font-serif font-bold text-9xl text-neutral-900">404</h1>
    <p class="col-start-4 col-span-6 font-serif font-semibold text-2xl text-neutral-900 opacity-50">Page not found.</p>
